  <description><![CDATA[<p>As a ski-inclusive hotel this property offers great value for money and everything you need for a fabulous week skiing the 3 valleys. Children's clubs and a great entertainment programmes are also included providing a great choice for families and groups alike. Views from the property are stunning and can be enjoyed from the sun terrace or relax with a drink in the lounge (with Wi-Fi) after a long day exploring one of the best ski areas in Europe! Children's clubs are available from 3 months to 17 years and start on Monday.* For children from 3-5 years (Club des Malins), ski club (Piou Piou) is included in the mornings. The rest of the day is taken up with games in the snow, sledging, music, drama, creative games, and reading. The club runs from 8:30am to 6pm and also 7pm to 9pm.</p>
<p>For children from 6-10 years (Club des Copains), activities include igloo making, sledging, snow shoeing and creative games. The club runs from 8:30am to 6pm and also 7pm to 9pm. Club Ados is for teenagers from 11-17 years and runs from 9:30am to 9pm. The morning is spent skiing. In the afternoon, they have a varied programme of activities with music and dancing in the evening. For adults (intermediate level and above) a Discovery Day is provided by an ESF instructor during French holidays.</p>
<p>*(Children from 3 months to 2 years must provide a certificate of health on arrival).</p>]]></description>
