  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>All rooms have bath with shower head attachment or shower room, WC, telephone, hairdryer (on request) and cable / satellite TV with English speaking channels.</p>
<ul>
<li>Twin room (A2): sleeps 2 people (17m²) in twin beds. Also available for sole occupancy, on request (F1)</li>
<li>Triple room (B3): sleeps 3 people (17m²) in a double bed with additional single top bunk bed (suitable for a child from 6-12 years)</li>
<li>Quad room (C4): sleeps 4 people (34m²) in twin/double beds with a balcony and south facing views</li>
</ul>
<p>House keeping is included (once mid week). Under 13s must share a room with an adult.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
